dashboardConfig.gjs-css: * { box-sizing: border-box; } body {margin: 0;} *:focus { outline-offset: 2px; outline-color: rgba(0,132,255,0.2);} .no-events > * {pointer-events: none} [loader=in] {overflow: hidden;} .loader{position: absolute; top: 0; right:0; bottom: 0; left: 0; z-index: 99; display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);} .loader>.dot {margin: 5px; width: 24px; height: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; background: #0084ff; border-radius: 100%; display: inline-block; animation: slide 1s infinite;} .loader>.dot:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; background: #0084ff; } .loader>.dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; background: #339cff; } .loader>.dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; background: #66b5ff; } .loader>.dot:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; background: #99ceff; } .loader>.dot:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; background: #cce6ff; } @-moz-keyframes slide { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1.6); } 100% { transform: scale(1); }  } @-webkit-keyframes slide { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1.6); } 100% { transform: scale(1); }  } @-o-keyframes slide { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1.6); } 100% { transform: scale(1); }  } @keyframes slide { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1.6); } 100% { transform: scale(1); } } #wrapper{position:static;padding:0;overflow-x:auto;overflow-y:auto;}
dashboardConfig.gjs-html:
<script>

      
  if (window.spSocket) {
    function nav(url, isNewWindow) {
      if (isNewWindow) {
        window.open(url, '_blank');
      } else {
        window.location.href = url;
      }
    }

    window.spSocket.subscribe({ eventName: 'dashboard', callback: function(data) {
      if (!data) return;

      switch(data.type) {
        
      case 'dashboard.dom.updateAttr':
        var $comp = $(data.selector);

        if ($comp) {
          if (data.attrs && data.attrs instanceof Array) {
            data.attrs.forEach(function(attr) {
              Object.keys(attr).forEach(function(key) {
                $comp.attr(key, attr[key]);
              });
            });
          }
        }
        break;

    ;
        
    case 'dashboard.window.eval':
      var handleEvalResult = function(event) {
        if (event.data && event.data.type && event.data.type === "dashboard.window.eval") {
          if (event.data.err) {
            window.spSocket.send({ eventName: "dashboard", data: { type: "dashboard.window.evalResponse", err: event.data.err } });
            return;
          }
          window.spSocket.send({ eventName: "dashboard", data: { type: "dashboard.window.evalResponse", data: event.data.data } });
        }
      }
  
      var propertiesToCover = ["location"];
      var createSandboxContext = function(srcObj, propertiesToCover) {
        var context = {};
        Object.keys(srcObj).forEach(function (key) {
          if (srcObj.hasOwnProperty(key) && propertiesToCover.indexOf(key) > -1) {
            context[key] = srcObj[key];
          }
        });
        return context;
      }

      var createIframe = function() {
        var $iframe = document.getElementById("dashboard-sandbox");
        if (!$iframe) {
          $iframe = document.createElement("iframe");
          $iframe.setAttribute("id", "dashboard-sandbox");
          $iframe.setAttribute("sandbox", "allow-same-origin allow-scripts");
          $iframe.style.display = "none";
        }
        $iframe.innerHTML = "";

        return $iframe;
      };

      var initializeSandbox = function(code) {
        // var $iframe = createIframe();
        var $script = document.getElementById('sandbox');

        if (!$script) {
          $script = document.createElement("script");
          $script.setAttribute('id', 'sandbox');
        }

        $script.innerText = '(function() { return eval(' + code + ') })()';

        document.body.appendChild($script);

        // $iframe.contentWindow.addEventListener("message", handleEvalResult, false);
        // $iframe.contentWindow.sandboxContext = createSandboxContext(window, propertiesToCover);
        // $iframe.contentDocument.body.appendChild($script);
      }

      initializeSandbox(data.code);
      break;

  ;
        
    case 'dashboard.component.show':
      var $comp = $('#' + data.componentId);
      if ($comp) {
          $comp.show();
      }
      break;

  ;
        
    case 'dashboard.component.hide':
      var $comp = $('#' + data.componentId);
      if ($comp) {
          $comp.hide();
      }
      break;

  ;
      }
    }})
  }

    
</script>
